While you are waiting for the class or trying to get qualified to go to school, advance sent your license application. Get this all done before going to school. Your time is a very valuable asset, you need it to make money somewhere.

Now that you finished school your best bet is to go for converting engineers licenses. They are pretty much the fastest to acquire and also has a high turnover in them. This means that you could be in and out of this class (if you are fast) in 6 months or less. Explaining in detail, converting engineers licenses are about 3-4 week course to complete, and when you graduate you have to go through the final part of this course.
